place.name: OLDHAMSTOCKS
place.gazetteerText: Oldhamstocks, vil., Haddingtonshire, and par., partly also in Berwickshire, on Oldhamstock Burn - par., 8837 ac., pop. 568; vil., 3 miles W. of Cockburns-path; P.O. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
